    "description": "<blockquote><p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Ace of Cards</strong>, <strong>Darkblade</strong>, <strong>Entropist</strong>, and <strong>Spiritist</strong>, and you must have acquired the <strong>Magic Cards</strong> Skill. <br /></p></blockquote><p>When you resolve the <strong>Double Trouble</strong> effect, you may have all of its damage become <strong>light</strong> or <strong>dark</strong> (instead of being of a type matching the <strong>suits</strong> of the resolved cards).</p><p>Additionally, as long as there is a <strong>joker</strong> in your <strong>discard pile</strong>, all damage dealt by your <strong>Blinding Flush</strong>, <strong>Double Trouble</strong>, and <strong>Magic Flush</strong> effects ignores Immunities and Resistances.</p>",
